    slug: 'managing-screen-time-children-practical-guide',
    title: 'Managing Screen Time for Children: A Practical Guide for Parents',
    category: 'Parent Guidance',
    excerpt: 'Screen time is one of the most debated topics in modern parenting. This evidence-based guide helps parents set healthy boundaries, have productive conversations, and support their child\'s wellbeing.',
    metaDescription: 'A practical guide to managing children\'s screen time based on the latest research. Includes age-appropriate limits, strategies for reducing conflict, and tips for building healthy digital habits.',
